# Web App Conventions

`apps/web` is a Next.js 16.2.4 App Router app with React 19, Tailwind CSS 4, and Clerk.

Check current local Next docs under `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` before changing routing, middleware, caching, server actions, or other Next-specific APIs.

- Keep public marketing routes under `src/app/(marketing)`.
- Keep authenticated product routes under `src/app/(app)`.
- Preserve `src/middleware.ts` protection for `/(app)(.*)` unless auth boundaries intentionally change.
- Use Clerk APIs from `@clerk/nextjs` and `@clerk/nextjs/server`.
- Keep user-facing copy in Portuguese when the surrounding UI is Portuguese.
- Reuse `@meicontrol/ui` and `@meicontrol/types` instead of redefining shared UI or fiscal domain types.

Validate focused web changes with:

```bash
pnpm turbo run lint --filter=@meicontrol/web
pnpm turbo run build --filter=@meicontrol/web
```
